  "texts": [
    "LayoutTransformer [53] leverages self-attention to learn and understand the existing relationships between regions in a given layout.",
    "The authors based the generation of new scientific papers on data in the PubLayNet [49] dataset.",
    "Inspired by this work, we proposed an approach to generate layout and content of scientific papers in high-resolution PDF format [54], filling the regions with generated text and tables and images crawled from [55].",
    "DiscussionOne of the most challenging aspects when creating a new dataset is how to annotate the data, to scale with the dimension of the collection and include in the data a good amount of variability.",
    "Manual annotations are time consuming and expensive, but ensure good quality; on the contrary, automatic procedures can generate more annotated data, but require often human intervention due to errors."
